Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you all ready?\NThere's no need to be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hairband is crooked.\NI'll fix it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way. Very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.99,0:00:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now. Hold my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lieberts, who defected from\NEast Germany a few days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,have appeared together\Nas a family for the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:00:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. and Mrs. Liebert didn't appear tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and their fraternal twins\Nboth appeared happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.82,0:01:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Liebert,\Nhow do you like it in the West?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.82,0:01:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually rather complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.66,0:01:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.78,0:01:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When I realize that I'm free\Nto speak as I please,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it's difficult to find the words to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.46,0:01:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But to answer your question,\Njust look at the smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,on the faces of my wife and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears your children are\Nenjoying their freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.01,0:01:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it appears so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you please tell us about\Nwhat life is like in the East now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.77,0:01:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. It's yours, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! An acorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, one more time. Which is it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. It's yours, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan, open up both your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, you're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've won either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,\Nall the acorns here are yours, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Johan, did you see the town\Nfrom the car on our way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way different than on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There were lots of pretty shops.\NAnd there are lots of clothes and toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw it too, right, Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all yours too, Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They are?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How come they're mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you on TV, Mr. Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan, did someone come?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you… do this, Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ones before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When Uncle Josef and Aunt Klara died,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and when Mr. Baedeker died,\Nyou did all those too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the monster came today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed all of them, didn't you, Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster came to take us away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Put out your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,After you shoot me, wipe off the gun\Nwith a cloth and toss it out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you shoot me in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,After you shoot me, run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Run as fast as you can\Nso the monster doesn't catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Even when I'm dead,\Nyou are me and I am you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That night…\NThat rainy night, someone came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone came to the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone… Someone came. Who were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:08:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster came.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How come this mansion caught fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody was living here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They think it was arson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's disturbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you please come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,General Wolf wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,General… Wolf…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,General Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you were summoned as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a letter from Johan saying,\N"I'll be waiting at the Red Rose Mansion."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But just getting to this hospital\Nhere in Prague was the best I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get a letter as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the only person who ever\Nwrites letters to me anymore is Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Try not to talk so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born into a military family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.16,0:09:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was part of my destiny\Nto be one of the elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, the only person who knows\Nwho I am is that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that\Nthe Red Rose Mansion burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet that at this very moment,\Nthey're coming into the light of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people whose names\Nwere stolen just like mine was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you identified\Nwhere the fire started?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It seems to have been\Nin a large hall on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the flames were most intense there,\Nkerosene or gas must have been used.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kerosene?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it was arson, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't know for sure\Nuntil we investigate further.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But a wall of the hall was torn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw something under the rose bush,\Nthen when I dug,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I just kept on finding more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,After all these years,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll finally come to the light of day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no longer anyone alive\Nwho knows their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This mansion was our only clue\Nto Tenma's whereabouts, but now…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way! Coming through! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact HQ! It's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We've found a bunch of human bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,46 people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1981,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,46 people suddenly disappeared\Nfrom that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, that was all the information\NI could get in East Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,An experiment was being conducted\Nat that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,An experiment…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Get these onlookers out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that is where\Nthat child was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan… I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't walk anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan, will we… die?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan, say my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Say my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have names.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Say my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My name…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-Get some blankets.\N-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-And something warm to drink.\N-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,THE NAMELESS MONSTER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"Such a shame because Johan\Nwas such a wonderful name."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Those children didn't have names.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When I gave him the name Johan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it must have awakened\Nsomething inside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All this talk of the past is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I have no future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, General Wolf.\NDon't talk anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Heinemann is…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Heinemann is with\Nthe other members of our organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Our organization was\Nmade up of four people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There was\Nthe murdered Professor Goedelitz and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva is with the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to use Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let them meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether I'm dead or alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no stopping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about to go out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to save us, Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:15:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Helmut.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmut Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who knew me as Helmut…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,are no longer alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Say my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That proves that I lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmut.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.79,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Say my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmut!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Helmut Wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be…\Nthe landscape that Johan saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A world where there are no names.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,General Wolf…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The gate is locked too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The police are\Nprobably keeping people out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Lipský…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that this was important to you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,since you listened\Nto book readings here as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-But--\N-Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was important to you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It could have been a place\Nthat would revive your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My vision…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of the great hall in this mansion\Nfilled with bodies lying in a heap…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The vision you saw, Nina,\Nit happened, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised when I saw the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:17:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they found 46 skeletons\Nat the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just like\Nyour brother Johan told you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What did my brother Johan see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A horrific sight… True fear…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had been there… at that time…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have turned into a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, it may be good\Nthat this place burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be\Nmore difficult for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I wouldn't be able to live\Nif this place disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't feel that way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably because\Nthis place held only sad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't a gifted student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That made me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able\Nto live up to his expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That made me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wished…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wished that I lived up\Nto his expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I became an unwanted child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Lipský, do you have a mom and dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But I've never lived with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you regain your memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope they're happy memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Happy memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I have any happy memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma once told me…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,if you don't have any happy memories,\Nthen make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma told me you can make happy memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dieter, your mouth is covered in ketchup.\N-So is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.28,0:19:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making a new puppet show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's ever liked watching\Nmy puppet shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think people will like this new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us your new show!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I wanna see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a girl who's lost her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I dream that a monster is chasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I dream that I'm chasing a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I love singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I also love dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, I'll have a lovely dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, that dream will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of what comes next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the story of this girl\Nto have a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.71,0:20:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I want it to have a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I want it to have a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl decided to leave on a voyage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She does not know\Nwhat kind of voyage it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She does not know what awaits her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But the girl will\Ncourageously continue her journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl turned around\Nand waved again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she left…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In search of a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina! You came--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.62,0:22:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you, Mr. Lipský.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.92,0:22:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the son of the owner
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Red Rose Mansion,\NFranz Bonaparta, aren't you?
